				Ok..Here is the deal.  Her PH's (Place Holders) are the Giant Widow Spiders that spawn right right around the same area that she spawns.  Just have a Druid or Ranger track your party to them.  There are about 4-5 of them.  You might have to kill them all twice.  She cons blue to lvl 45 and she can be quite nasty.  Our Party consisted of a 45 Warrior, 45 Ranger, and 51 Druid.  We killed her three times without dying, but once she got close to simply meleeing me (Ranger) to death.  The last time, our Druid took her down by herself.  A successful root then two sold nukes did the trick.  <BR>
